                           What will happen if I accept a challenge?
                        </button>

                        <div id="faq5" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" >
                          <div class="card-body">
                            Once you accept a challenge, Arena will launch the quiz for the challenged level-difficulty and on completion of the quiz your new score will become valid and the challenge will be removed from your challenges.
                          </div>
                        </div>
    
  					</div><!--Card Close-->                                  
			</div><!--Accordion 5 close-->   
            
            
            
            <div class="accordion">       
                  <div class="card">

                        <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#faq6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                           What will happen if I accept a challenge and quit?
                        </button>

                        <div id="faq6" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" >
                          <div class="card-body">
                            Your attempt will not hold valid and the challenge will still show up in your challenges.
                          </div>
                        </div>
    
  					</div><!--Card Close-->                                  
			</div><!--Accordion 6 close--> 
            
            
            
            <div class="accordion">       
